  <name>SiriKali</name>
  <summary>Manage user encrypted directories</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Sirikali provides a Qt/C++ GUI front end to sshfs, fscrypt, cryfs, gocryptfs, securefs and encfs, allowing the user to create, mount, and unmount encrypted volumes.</p>
    <p>It works well together with cloud services like Dropbox, iCloud, OneDrive and others.</p>
  </description>
